      "index": 1,
      "text": "This is the 'Icebox' prison, it was established on Weldry after the coup by Director Espinosa to interrogate and hold anyone who opposed his rule, with many not surviving its brutal conditions.\n\nIt was built on a former Liao fortress that once served as the planetary garrison, so just approaching it would be extremely difficult.",
