      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c83c621b3510cdccc61ed5c"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Those walls may look tough but the recent fall of Tikonov to the AFFS showed that even the strongest anti-'Mech fortifications aren't enough to stop a determined attacker.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
