      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c64226bed1d5a9caab64875"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Good, because I am not even sure I could land safely close to that stronghold, with the amount of turrets we've detected so far.\n\nPossible, yes but also risky as well, not to mention the potential size of the garrison we'd facing on the ground.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
