      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c88015c7994746d190d8381"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "So our mission is either to assassinate or capture him?\n\nI'd prefer some payback for what he did to Commander Markham because the boss never got a chance to fight back.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "And he also got Raju Mastiff killed in front of me.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 11,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c94d1aa42fda002e7dee5b6"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
