      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf0ee6a3b30556132405eb5"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Considering who he is, I also doubt the Captain wants him killed, or at least until she pries out of his head all the Directorate's secrets.\n\nSo this should be an 'black bag' job, although he should also be well guarded.",
      "branches": [
        {
