      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c21045fe0cebbffd8fa4845"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Colonel Haust is currently at Weldry, supervising the reopening of the 'Icebox' and according to our sources, also conducting some illegal operations of his own.\n\nThe Fourth Succession War has made war profiteering very lucrative, as we've seen on Lyreton.",
